  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a libxcvt</title>

    <para>
      <application>libxcvt</application> is a library providing a standalone
version of the X server implementation of the VESA CVT standard timing
modelines generator. It is meant to be a direct replacement to the version
formerly provided by the Xorg server.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

